NAME
    IPC::Run::Patch::Setuid - Set EUID

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.003 of IPC::Run::Patch::Setuid (from
    Perl distribution IPC-Run-Patch-Setuid), released on 2019-04-30.

SYNOPSIS
     use IPC::Run::Patch::Setuid -euid => 1000;

DESCRIPTION
    This patch sets EUID of the child process ($>) to the specified ID after
    forking.

CONFIGURATION
  -euid
    Unsigned integer.

  -egid
    String. Either a single GID or multiple GID separated by space.

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/IPC-Run-Patch-Setuid>.

